From: 
To: Nathan NYSD Chambers 
Cc: 
Jeff 
Pa Inca 
Subject: US v. Maxwell - Letter re Minor Victim-3 
Date: Sun, 07 Nov 2021 16:55:12 +0000 
Attachments: Govit_Letter_re_MV-3_and_VictimdFinal].pdf 
Chambers, 
Attached please find a letter in response to the Court's order yesterday regarding Minor Victim-3. The Government is not 
seeking redactions but is filing this letter temporarily under seal to permit the defense an opportunity to seek redactions, 
and pending the Court's resolution of the Government's other redaction requests. 
Respectfully submitted, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
New York, New York 10007 
EFTA00021977
